Deploying the Astrogrid test Portal                              BKM 20030326

1) Install apache tomcat (current version is 4.1.18)

2) Copy Astrogrid.war into $CATALINA_HOME/webapps

3) Start tomcat

4) Point browser at http:/<machine name>:8080/Astrogrid

The Astrogrid test portlet is on the home (anon user) page. This page cannot
be edited to add or remove portlets. If you wish to do this login as one
of turbine/turbine or astrogrid/astrogrid or create your OWN username. To
do this attempt to login with an unknown username and the option to "create
an account" will appear.

All other source files in this directory are presented for reference only.
An ant build file to use them sensible will appear soon!
